latestIgtvVideos.caption:
What I love the most about these products is that they contain simple and straight to the point ingredients that target my dark spots. They worked well for my sensitive skin which is a plus point☺️ Personally, I noticed an improvement in my skin texture and also noticed a glow on my skin🤍 

The healing kit aims to:
-reduce blemishes
-remove dead skin cells
-reduce dark spots and hyperpigmentation 
-promote a radiant and glowy complexion 

My favourite product has to be the Healing Face Ubtan!✨ It contains Saffron, Orange Peel, Rose Petals and of course Turmeric which helps to exfoliate my skin without being too harsh. After washing it off, my skin doesn’t feel dry or tight but rather nourished. After moisturising, I notice a subtle glow on my face and my skin feels extremely soft. Y’all should definitely check this range out!🌻 You won’t regret it 💛
